{"id":591295,"date":[{"year":1980,"month":2,"day":24}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"209","ytitle":"","mtitle":"豫园春","ftitle":"","authors":["朱金晨"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱金晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九曲桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徜徉在九曲桥上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花怎能不打湿心怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回首追溯过去的年头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我的祖国，我的上海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不正是从这座桥上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲曲弯弯地走过来……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖心事品茶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到这里请随意点茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必挑那龙井、茉莉……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧地重游一样的味觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要品吗?话儿全泡在壶里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日，再上乘的茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃在嘴里也是苦涩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今儿，再劣等的茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呷在舌尖也是香馥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绢花·鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一家店专售绢花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一家店专售鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样都是为了爱美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却走着不同的步伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人跨进这家……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人来到那家……"}]}